{"TopicId":189197,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Kerbal engineering redux\u0026#039; hud overlapping with altitude meter?","CreatedByName":"paul23","CreatedById":120544,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-23T00:10:11Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"paul23","CreatedById":120544,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-23T00:10:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m wondering what setting I have wrong, but quite \u0022often\u0022 (happens not always, and sometimes it just works correctly), the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Engineer Redux (mod)\u0022\u003EKER\u003C/abbr\u003E hud display is overlapping with the altimeter, and seems to be \u0022out of position\u0022. (shifted to the right).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nExample:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022SkFPpAn.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/SkFPpAn.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat is causing this? (And why does it happen only like 70% of the time).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust for information: I\u0027m using ksp 1.7.3\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-10-23T00:10:42Z\u0022 title=\u002210/23/2019 12:10  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 23, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by paul23\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vorg","CreatedById":74652,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-23T19:50:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can move those little windows. I forget how off hand but there is setting that unlocks them and then you can move them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"paul23","CreatedById":120544,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-24T13:28:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUh I\u0027m talking about the hud displays at the top. I cannot find a setting where I can move those though, been looking for quite a while.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"maja","CreatedById":168379,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-24T13:32:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223693919\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022189197\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221571923733\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022120544\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022paul23\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, paul23 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUh I\u0027m talking about the hud displays at the top. I cannot find a setting where I can move those though, been looking for quite a while.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHud1 and Hud2 in the list of \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Engineer Redux (mod)\u0022\u003EKER\u003C/abbr\u003E windows (Orbital, Vessel etc.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"paul23","CreatedById":120544,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-24T13:33:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223693923\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022189197\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221571923953\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022168379\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022maja\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, maja said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHud1 and Hud2 in the list of \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Engineer Redux (mod)\u0022\u003EKER\u003C/abbr\u003E windows (Orbital, Vessel